    dc:creator "Teruel, Rolando; Kovařík, František; Lowe, Graeme; Šťáhlavský, František" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of the remarkable scorpion genus Megacormus Karsch, 1881 (Scorpiones: Euscorpiidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8222216>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8222218> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8222216>
    dc:description "Figures 27–34: Megacormus seductus sp. n. Figures 27–28. Male holotype, carapace and tergites I–IV (27) and coxosternal area and sternites (28). Figures 29–34. Female paratype, carapace and tergites I–IV (29), coxosternal area and sternites (30), and left legs I–IV, retrolateral aspect (31–34)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8222216/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8222218>
    dc:description "Figures 35–42. Megacormus seductus sp. n. Figures 35, 37–39. Male holotype, telson in lateral (35), metasoma and telson in lateral (37), dorsal (38) and ventral (39) views. Figures 36, 40–42. Female paratype, telson in lateral (36), metasoma and telson in lateral (40), dorsal (41) and ventral (42) views. Scale bars: 10 mm (37–39, 40–42)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8222218/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

